'''國浩大廈'''（{{lang-en|Guoco Tower}}），2016年落成，是[[混合用途開發|混合用途開發]]的[[摩天大樓|摩天大樓]]，位於[[新加坡|新加坡]][[丹戎巴葛|丹戎巴葛]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/high-hopes-singapore-s-upcoming-tallest-building-aims-to-rejuven-8215492|title=High hopes: Singapore's upcoming tallest building aims to rejuvenate Tanjong Pagar|publisher=[[Channel_NewsAsia|Channel NewsAsia]]|date=13 January 2016|first=Patrick John|last=Lim|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2018-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052639/https://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/business/high-hopes-singapore-s-upcoming-tallest-building-aims-to-rejuven-8215492|dead-url=no}}</ref>，樓高{{convert|283.7|m}}，是[[新加坡摩天大樓列表|新加坡現時最高的建築物]]，打破了[[萊佛士坊一號|萊佛士坊一號]]、[[大華銀行大廈|大華銀行大廈]]及[[共和大廈|共和大廈]]共同保持了20年的紀錄<ref name=straitstimes1>{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/business/tanjong-pagar-centre-new-tallest-building-in-singapore-after-20-years|title=Tanjong Pagar Centre: New tallest building in Singapore after 20 years|work=[[The_Straits_Times|The Straits Times]]|date=14 January 2016|first=Rennie|last=Whang|access-date=2021-03-29|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927114719/https://www.straitstimes.com/business/tanjong-pagar-centre-new-tallest-building-in-singapore-after-20-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

